EXPLANATION
BY THE LEGISLATIVE COUNCIL
OF
A N A C T
RELATING TO GENERAL ASSEMBLY -- COMMITTEES AND STAFF
***
1 This act would require any nonprofit, as a condition for requesting state funds from the
2 general assembly, to submit and to post on their website, a detailed list of ten of their highest paid
3 director, officer and employee salaries, and any forms of compensation provided to those
4 individuals. It would further require the disclosure to include fundraising, endowments, trusts,
5 memorial giving and/or any and all activities that fund the nonprofit.
6 This act would take effect upon passage.
